Detailed Description

Identifier for a specific application component (core::Page, core::Delegate, core::Subscriber, or content::ContentProvider) that is available.

Two pieces of information, encapsulated here, are required to identify a component: the package (a String) it exists in, and the class (a String) name inside of that package. 

 Demand demand;
 demand.setClassName("MyPackage", "MyClass");
 ComponentName component = demand.getComponent();
 String strPackage = component.getPackageName();
 String strPackage = component.getClassName();
